summary: I just watched the last episode to season 1 of SW Resistance and I have to say I'm impressed with Kaz's plan. This show has...
body:
I just watched the last episode to season 1 of SW Resistance and I have to say I’m impressed with Kaz’s plan. This show has gotten so much better since the first few episodes and I can’t wait to see what happens in the next season.

I just hope we get to see Black One.
